Martial Arts Champion...

17:50.709 --> 17:51.667
Kai.

17:51.750 --> 17:53.250
Would you please come up here?

17:59.834 --> 18:01.333
I'm gonna go congratulate Kai.

18:09.375 --> 18:10.667
Congratulations, Kai.

18:11.458 --> 18:13.500
