I planned the attack against you.

19:45.125 --> 19:48.041
- Just don't let me fall.
- Don't worry. I've got you, man.

19:48.125 --> 19:50.208
Come on. Get up.

19:51.000 --> 19:52.208
Come on-- Over.

19:59.667 --> 20:02.458
That proves you're weak.

20:03.875 --> 20:05.208
