Uh, excuse me, my wife has a name.

21:06.917 --> 21:09.125
Yeah, I may not know what it is,
but she has a name.

21:10.250 --> 21:11.583
They're not our wives.

21:11.667 --> 21:15.041
We're 13, there were no rings
and one of us was dressed like Elvis.

21:15.709 --> 21:18.834
Oh, really?
